All of us, if we have been following the papers at all, are fully aware that new directions will be established, and Jack and Sam, after thirty years of leadership, not only intend to maintain their position, but feel that they owe it to their clientele to protect them, more than ever, in terms of quality and price. If my barometer reads correctly, you can
